				<td colspan="2"><span>I have joked with my wife about this before and came up with a kind of rolling chant... depending on my twist:
<br />

<br />
fasterfasterfaster                          (rizlona's)
<br />
S...l...o...w, s...l...o...w                 (snare slow)
<br />
die! die! die!                                 (DD or Dot)
<br />
sparkle:) sparkle:)                         (PoV)
<br />

<br />
then repeat (of course)
<br />

<br />
Thats not an actual twist I use, but you get the gist of it <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" /> 
