<br />
Harnessing energies using sonic waveforms.
<br />
Harmonic resonances and wotnot to disrupt organic tissues.
<br />
AND, we're using magic stuff like drums.
<br />
That would kinda work for fire/ice chants.  Fire effects is exciting molecles to cause heat, ice would be slowing particles (like Ben and Jerrys do in their fridges, they use high volumes of sound to cool)
<br />
Frequency of the chants for Disease effects, like the 'Brown Note' (Now that would be an AA worth getting...).  The US army did experients using certain frequencies to make people feel bad, then throw up, lose muscle control.
